er&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR25nDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=fd8fd613\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.soundcloud.com/iahc/usa-national-anthem-star-spangled-banner</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZykHbrV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZykHbrV.jpg&h=30a62641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全民發夢合唱</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">美國</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國歌</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> <span style=\"color: gold;\">We should learn how to sing</span><br />\n <em><span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;The Star-</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">Spangled Banner&quot;</span></em><br />\n</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528828</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家仲記唔記得手足揮美國國旗唱美國國歌唱到Trump Trump都retweet!!!!</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vNfTjAM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvNfTjAM.gif&h=db1663f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/dcexaminer/status/1161305213841682439?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdcexaminer%2Fstatus%2F1161305213841682439%3Fs%3D09&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR25nDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=3702e6da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdcexaminer%2Fstatus%2F1161305213841682439%3Fs%3D09&h=72f77df1\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/dcexaminer/status/1161305213841682439?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">除咗九月八日，如果<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">十月一日</span>我地再幫支共賀一賀佢，搞到全美國都知支共國慶我地用美國國歌慶祝，你話會激到維尼幾咁高興？<br />\n<br />\n而最重要，我地之前揮動美國國旗、唱美國國歌，美國傳媒一直都理解成我地係以追求人權民主自由既普世價值而表態！！！亦係動之以情地令佢地推動 香港民主及人權法案 既方法！！！<br />\n</span> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n九月八日發夢同我一齊唱！<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">MV with Lyrics: </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vPKp29Luryc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvPKp29Luryc&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR25nDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=2f998ae7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vPKp29Luryc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">歌詞：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5nSVsMz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5nSVsMz.png&h=279e88f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F1sKkdk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF1sKkdk.gif&h=5c4ce310&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Liberate Hong Kong, <br />\nthe Revolution of Our Times<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Make Hong Kong great again!</span><br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"8e4aa6fc3332438c8121783d61eb2f083dd7edb9","tid":1531931,"uid":116328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:19:46.000Z","msg":"四"},{"pid":"54ee2f2b79986dbe93ccd6e40a5dbbafd9b52509","tid":1531931,"uid":116328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:20:04.000Z","msg":"五"},{"pid":"abddea76fe0c090929ed6dc5a3029341aad1ddd4","tid":1531931,"uid":6063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:20:12.000Z","msg":"黑警自編自導自演暴力示威，尋求警獨<br />\n<br />\n每次示威既衝擊，暴力都有直接間接証據証明係由臥底警察直接參與，策劃或者扇動。表面係想挑起市民同政府對立，直接令到件事收唔到科。<br />\n<br />\n我懷疑係警察部高層同政府高層之間既權力鬥爭，目的係為警察部爭取更大權力，甚至變為影子政府。<br />\n<br />\n由獨立薪酬表， 獨立財務報表，到藉住緊急法直接動員各政府其他部門既人力及資源，收編保安局，到最後凌駕3司11局成為幕後政府。<br />\n<br />\n由於警隊係香港唯一武裝力量，而其中一個制衡方法就係引入另一股武裝力量，例如又藉緊急法引入解放軍/武警 到香港。你見到建制派一路吹風，其實葉劉一水人可能都有同樣睇法。<br />\n<br />\n我就冇証冇據，純粹ff出黎既，大家點睇呢個議題有冇得發揮呢？<br />\n<br />\n巴打我地既諗法異曲同工，略同啊"},{"pid":"39467c160a25c340b2475bd4fd13f6e44db29bb9","tid":1531931,"uid":116328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:20:15.000Z","msg":"六"},{"pid":"6b2f54f19577ed55d01a55d03921c69d57302efd","tid":1531931,"uid":134744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:20:44.000Z","msg":"有冇得聽日記者會叫記者問下？"},{"pid":"a9dd0001b9305093f5a288e0afb2cff36cb61187","tid":1531931,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:21:01.000Z","msg":"狼 來 了 source"},{"pid":"d8f7de5a08ce28ade6f28c63e39995ca9a2171e0","tid":1531931,"uid":212238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:21:30.000Z","msg":"又封鐵，想人拆埋商場？"},{"pid":"a6064a7173b3e2b3d46661598fd8bcbd1a95da4c","tid":1531931,"uid":116328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9dd0001b9305093f5a288e0afb2cff36cb61187","tid":1531931,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:21:01.000Z","msg":"狼 來 了 source"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:21:45.000Z","msg":"搵次上街就會見到直直直"},{"pid":"968dada91b625691d830ca4599b28bfc26160d48","tid":1531931,"uid":287496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:21:50.000Z","msg":"無人機準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7082658ebe1b7da4fc8b592086e0b437fc0469e8","tid":1531931,"uid":41458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:23:58.000Z","msg":"灑藍色粉係唔合理嘅<br />\n因為有風，大風可以吹好遠，吹到九龍都唔奇<br />\n根本冇可能可以確定到係示威者<br />\n<br />\nPouring blue fluorescent powders from the heli is bullshit<br />\nIt's because of the wind can blow those powder far away from the protest area. It is completely ridiculous to say that heli released powders from the sky. It just makes no sense."},{"pid":"8c12b976bb4f370745e1078f867b4a4b0312bb1d","tid":1531931,"uid":36113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:24:16.000Z","msg":"理閪佢放乜粉，你話會中毒就話驚姐<br />\n若果只係for marking，驚閪咩，全部人捉哂去坐監囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"418f3cc888bb61cf0424e0cf56daf19b254561a0","tid":1531931,"uid":47202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:24:42.000Z","msg":"有冇辦法令直升機唔敢靠近？"},{"pid":"28e99389dc8ab477f73d1ee2a1297824174d1341","tid":1531931,"uid":282118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abddea76fe0c090929ed6dc5a3029341aad1ddd4","tid":1531931,"uid":6063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:20:12.000Z","msg":"黑警自編自導自演暴力示威，尋求警獨<br />\n<br />\n每次示威既衝擊，暴力都有直接間接証據証明係由臥底警察直接參與，策劃或者扇動。表面係想挑起市民同政府對立，直接令到件事收唔到科。<br />\n<br />\n我懷疑係警察部高層同政府高層之間既權力鬥爭，目的係為警察部爭取更大權力，甚至變為影子政府。<br />\n<br />\n由獨立薪酬表， 獨立財務報表，到藉住緊急法直接動員各政府其他部門既人力及資源，收編保安局，到最後凌駕3司11局成為幕後政府。<br />\n<br />\n由於警隊係香港唯一武裝力量，而其中一個制衡方法就係引入另一股武裝力量，例如又藉緊急法引入解放軍/武警 到香港。你見到建制派一路吹風，其實葉劉一水人可能都有同樣睇法。<br />\n<br />\n我就冇証冇據，純粹ff出黎既，大家點睇呢個議題有冇得發揮呢？<br />\n<br />\n巴打我地既諗法異曲同工，略同啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:25:15.000Z","msg":"柒婆嘅保安正正係g4"},{"pid":"dc43999224a7d186043ff77e8f8ca830b39faecd","tid":1531931,"uid":282289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:25:18.000Z","msg":"疑點五個<br />\n1. 今日有雨有風，落粉係咪guarantee中target?<br />\n2. 落粉要高命中率一定要短時間大量投放，一定有人注意到先<br />\n3. 張相手腕係貼腰嗰一面，唔專登反轉手掌再前伸冇可能食粉<br />\n4. 張相嘅粉集中得黎又密，高空落粉可以apply得咁密?<br />\n5. 張相雨褸完全冇粉(唔排除洗甩咗但唔專登洗應該會有可觀份量殘留)?"},{"pid":"d5861c963c1a01e29515fedc40f875659d05d9aa","tid":1531931,"uid":282289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:29:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>疑點五個<br />\n1. 今日有雨有風，落粉點樣<span style=\"color: red;\">guarantee唔會中non-target</span>?<br />\n2. 落粉要高命中率一定要短時間大量投放，一定有人注意到先<br />\n3. 張相手腕係貼腰嗰一面，唔專登反轉手掌再前伸嘅話極難食粉<br />\n4. 張相嘅粉集中得黎又密，高空落粉可以apply得咁密?<br />\n5. 張相雨褸完全冇粉(唔排除洗甩咗但唔專登洗應該會有可觀份量殘留)?</blockquote><br />\n打錯第一條"},{"pid":"8c82fd5539c1a0dc7231fd34deeb5cff24996f8e","tid":1531931,"uid":282347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:32:10.000Z","msg":"發夢見到有RPG<br />\n<br />\nRole played games"},{"pid":"5161a39a9ecdf27e9ecf5aa1e78667abde5cabaa","tid":1531931,"uid":275243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:32:45.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n無論點正苦無啦啦出直升機點都會有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n灑粉太唔合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淋顏色水其實都係<br />\n始終你一散落黎無可能確保100%命中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n效果比水炮車差太多<br />\n大家一齊集思廣益下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nI agree with you<br />\nThe government deployed helicopters for some reasons<br />\nbut it is unrealistic to pour out fluorescent powder or coloured water<br />\nas you cannot guarantee that only protestors will be stained<br />\nwater cannon is a much simpler solution<br />\nlet's gather our thoughts<br />\n(Dear foreign friends do you have any idea?)"},{"pid":"cafc060514885c804cc354348138ba32208126df","tid":1531931,"uid":116328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7082658ebe1b7da4fc8b592086e0b437fc0469e8","tid":1531931,"uid":41458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:23:58.000Z",